message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE". The paper focuses on natural language question answering using neural networks and knowledge bases, which falls under the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE) which are relevant sub-categories.
